text: Oliver Đokić (; also transliterated Oliver Djokić; born 12 August 1981) is a Serbian football midfielder who plays for Radnički Svilajnac in Serbian League East. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:People from Svilajnac Category:Association football midfielders Category:Serbian footballers Category:FK Smederevo players Category:Serbian SuperLiga players
